<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>مَوْضُوعَةٌ حاضرة بين أيديهم.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>١٥-<span class="c5"> وَنَمارِقُ مَصْفُوفَةٌ:</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
